WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.740
<i>Previously on "zero hour"...</i>

00:01.775 --> 00:03.344
they didn't want the cross.

00:03.380 --> 00:06.460
You think they're after
the blood of christ?

00:06.495 --> 00:08.757
A blueprint
for the son of god.

00:08.792 --> 00:10.606
why would laila
betray hank?

00:10.641 --> 00:12.385
my position
with the shepherds

00:12.420 --> 00:15.220
Requires that I follow orders
on blind faith.

00:15.255 --> 00:18.020
Regardless of what I've done,
what I am doing now

00:18.055 --> 00:19.865
I'm doing to save your life.

00:19.900 --> 00:23.580
And when the time comes,
I won't flinch.

00:23.615 --> 00:24.665
your father achieved

00:24.700 --> 00:26.060
The first cloning
of a human being.

00:26.095 --> 00:27.785
<i>He created you.</i>

00:27.820 --> 00:30.780
You were the only man who could
complete this project.

00:30.815 --> 00:32.797
dad risked his life
for me.

00:32.832 --> 00:34.780
We are going to rescue him.

